0:01:12.646,000 --> 0:01:14,000
and you're never again going to create a book

20
0:01:14.813,000 --> 0:01:16,000
that anybody in the world cares about at all,

21
0:01:17.379,000 --> 0:01:19,000
ever again?"

22
0:01:19.879,000 --> 0:01:21,000
So that's reassuring, you know.

23
0:01:22.228,000 --> 0:01:24,000
