0:01:51.311,000 --> 0:01:52,000
(Laughter)

34
0:01:52.664,000 --> 0:01:53,000
Like that, you know.

35
0:01:54.516,000 --> 0:01:59,000
The answer -- the short answer to all those questions is, "Yes."

36
0:01:59.677,000 --> 0:02:01,000
Yes, I'm afraid of all those things.

37
0:02:01.977,000 --> 0:02:02,000
And I always have been.

38
0:02:03.242,000 --> 0:02:05,000
