0:02:54.852,000 --> 0:02:56,000
It just didn't come up like that, you know?

55
0:02:57.016,000 --> 0:03:,000
But to be fair, chemical engineers as a group

56
0:03:00.85,000 --> 0:03:02,000
haven't really earned a reputation over the centuries

57
0:03:03.398,000 --> 0:03:05,000
for being alcoholic manic-depressives.

58
0:03:06.094,000 --> 0:03:07,000
(Laughter)

59
0:03:07.542,000 --> 0:03:09,000
We writers, we kind of do have that reputation,

60
0:03:10.376,000 --> 0:03:13,000
and not just writers, but creative people across all genres,

61
0:03:14.359,000 --> 0:03:18,000
it seems, have this reputation for being enormously mentally unstable.

62
0:03:19.06,000 --> 0:03:22,000
And all you have to do is look at the very grim death count

63
0:03:22.876,000 --> 0:03:25,000
in the 20th century alone, of really magnificent creative minds

64
0:03:26.459,000 --> 0:03:29,000
who died young and often at their own hands, you know?

65
0:03:29.585,000 --> 0:03:32,000
