0:09:08.607,000 --> 0:09:11,000
Maybe go back to some more ancient understanding

177
0:09:12.003,000 --> 0:09:16,000
about the relationship between humans and the creative mystery.

178
0:09:16.504,000 --> 0:09:17,000
