196
0:10:11.921,000 --> 0:10:12,000
I had this encounter recently

197
0:10:13.697,000 --> 0:10:16,000
where I met the extraordinary American poet Ruth Stone,

198
0:10:17.406,000 --> 0:10:19,000
who's now in her 90s, but she's been a poet her entire life

199
0:10:20.241,000 --> 0:10:23,000
and she told me that when she was growing up in rural Virginia,

200
0:10:23.471,000 --> 0:10:24,000
she would be out working in the fields,

201
0:10:25.353,000 --> 0:10:27,000
and she said she would feel and hear a poem

202
0:10:28.229,000 --> 0:10:29,000
coming at her from over the landscape.

203
0:10:30.236,000 --> 0:10:33,000
